race.comment: FLOSS'S ONE (7) settled worse than midfield and struggled to get involved in an $80k 1200m feature at Port Macquarie last start. Has raced over 1000m here seven times for three wins and three minors. Very fit and from a good gate looks the testing material. SUPER IMPRESSIVE (6) missed the start then wound up powerfully to just miss out on an unlikely win when resuming over this distance at Port Macquarie last time out. Boasts a strong overall record and is in the right race to add to her impressive CV. THE ESCAPE (3) lines up for the first time since July 2024. Genuine sprinter who looks ready for a bright return judging by his big win in a recent Newcastle trial. FIFTEEN ROUNDS (2) is a greybeard with five top three finishes from nine attempts at today's journey. Racing well enough to play a key role today. MARKWELL DREAMER (5) is another veteran who is going okay and cannot be ruled out with the aid of a favourable gate.
